### Critical Bug Detail (Finding 1)
When user types `#task`, `thingQuery` is `""` → debounce fires `searchThings(' ')` → store guard `if (!query.trim()) return` short-circuits → `searchResults` stays `[]`. The `#type filter` footer hint advertises a feature that silently shows nothing. Fix: fall back to client-side filtering from the loaded `things` array when `typeFilter` is set but `thingQuery` is empty.

